    {
      "headings": [
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Actionable BI:"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Transform Your Data with Interactive Dashboards"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Empower business users"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Leverage visualizations & drive deeper insights"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Analyze trends and plan for the future"
        }
      ],
      "paragraphs": [
        "Being able to see the story within the data is crucial for every business’s success. Through data dashboards, interactive reports, charts, graphs, and other visual representations, you can see the big picture and make data-backed decisions.",
        "Folio3 offers cutting-edge data reporting & visualization services, powered by Microsoft, that empowers you to unlock the full potential of your data. Integrates with existing infrastructures, and provides customizable dashboards, to streamline your reporting architecture and visualize data in stunning, intuitive dashboards.",
        "Turn data into insightful charts and dashboards using drag and drop functionality",
        "Create charts, apply filters, and drill down to find answers and gain perspective on important data.",
        "Detect trends by comparing data across years of history and take proactive corrective measures to ensure your organization’s success."
      ],
      "listItems": [],
      "ctas": [
        {
          "text": "Request a call",
          "href": "#pgForm"
        }
      ],
      "images": [
        {
          "src": "https://azure.folio3.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/dvas-featured-img-1-1.webp",
          "alt": null,
          "w": 687,
          "h": 737
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "headings": [
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Building Automated ETL/ELT Pipelines"
        }
      ],
      "paragraphs": [
        "Join Us on the Journey Towards Success"
      ],
      "listItems": [],
      "ctas": [],
      "images": [
        {
          "src": "https://azure.folio3.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/elt-pipeline-diagram-1536x572.webp",
          "alt": null,
          "w": 1439,
          "h": 536
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "headings": [
        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Our Data Visualization Services"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Dashboard Optimization"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Dashboard Platform Migration"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Data Platform Implementation"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Report & Dashboard Development"
        }
      ],
      "paragraphs": [
        "Elevate your data presentation with our Dashboard Optimization service. We’ll fine-tune your existing dashboards pipelines, data models, visuals, and semantic layers, enhancing report load time, performance, and user experience. \n\n\n\n\nSTART YOUR PROJECT  > >",
        "Whether you're migrating from Tableau, Power BI, Qlik,  or Looker, our expert team ensures a smooth process, preserving data integrity and functionality. Experience the flexibility to switch between leading dashboard platforms effortlessly. \n\n\nSTART YOUR PROJECT  > >",
        "From data ingestion to visualization and advanced analytics, our services cover the end-to-end BI spectrum. We set up ETL/ELT processes, create a centralized repository, OLAP cubes, implement data security, and build interactive data dashboards \n\n\nSTART YOUR PROJECT  > >",
        "We build comprehensive &  tailored reports & dashboards for a variety of users including strategic, analytical, operational, and tactical dashboards. We help simplify complex datasets, uncover crucial trends, and track your Key Performance Indicators (KPIs).\n\n\nSTART YOUR PROJECT > >"
      ],
      "listItems": [],
      "ctas": [],
      "images": []
    },
    {
      "headings": [
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Dashboard Optimization"
        },
        {
          "tag": "h3",
          "text": "Dashboard Platform Migration"
        }
      ],
      "paragraphs": [
        "Elevate your data presentation with our Dashboard Optimization service. We’ll fine-tune your existing dashboards pipelines, data models, visuals, and semantic layers, enhancing report load time, performance, and user experience. \n\n\n\n\nSTART YOUR PROJECT  > >",
        "Whether you're migrating from Tableau, Power BI, Qlik,  or Looker, our expert team ensures a smooth process, preserving data integrity and functionality. Experience the flexibility to switch between leading dashboard platforms effortlessly. \n\n\nSTART YOUR PROJECT  > >"
      ],
