        {
          "tag": "h2",
          "text": "Discovery"
        }
      ],
      "paragraphs": [
        "Our subject matter experts engage in comprehensive sessions with you to gather insights,",
        "We craft detailed storyboards that outline the end-to-end appearance of the reports.",
        "Our experts identify and write down data pipelines and robust data models that serve",
        "Your dashboards are developed while implementing rigorous validation and testing processes",
        "After successful validation and testing of your reports, we deploy the finalized reports on your operational"
      ],
